org.gbif.ws.client

Class ClientBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.ws.client.ClientBuilder

  • public class ClientBuilder
extends Object
    ClientBuilder used to create Feign Clients. This builders support retry using exponential backoff and multithreaded http client.
